movies.title: Misteri janda kembang
movies.plot: A girl returns from the dead to gain her revenge on a gang of thugs that raped and murdered her.
movies.simplePlot: A girl returns from the dead to gain her revenge on a gang of thugs that raped and murdered her.

biography.placeOfBirth: Teloekbetoeng, Lampongsche Districten, Dutch East Indies [now Bandar Lampung, Lampung, Indonesia]
biography.bio: H.I.M. Damsyik was born on March 14, 1929 in Teloekbetoeng, Lampongsche Districten, Dutch East Indies as Haji Incik Muhammad Damsyik. He was an actor, known for Kembalinya si janda kembang (1992), Samson and Delilah (1987) and Satan's Slave (1982). He died on February 2, 2012 in South Jakarta, Indonesia.
biography.name: H.I.M. Damsyik

biography.bio: Fujiyanti is an actor, known for Bisa naik bisa turun (1991) and Misteri janda kembang (1991).
biography.name: Fujiyanti

biography.bio: Sally Marcellina was born on July 28, 1969 in Jakarta, Indonesia. She is an actress, known for Gadis metropolis (1991), Kembalinya si janda kembang (1992) and Pergaulan (1994).
biography.name: Sally Marcellina

biography.bio: Emri Margono is an actress, known for Mystics in Bali (1981), Aduh aduh mana tahan (1980) and Forgotten Rules (1990).
biography.name: Emri Margono

biography.bio: Simon P.S. is an actor, known for Senggol-senggolan (1980), The Hungry Snake Woman (1986) and Kamp tawanan wanita (1983).
biography.name: Simon P.S.

biography.bio: Teddy Prangi is an actor, known for Misteri janda kembang (1991) and I Love You (1989).
biography.name: Teddy Prangi
